query:
SELECT
                    CAST(
                        EXTRACT(
                            EPOCH FROM leaderboard.submitted_at
                        ) as bigint
                    ) as "timestamp!",
                    score,
                    pseudonym,
                    file_name as filename,
                    file_size as filesize
                FROM leaderboard
                INNER JOIN users
                    ON leaderboard.username=users.username
